Liquicity Records proudly presents her second album project "Escapism". Unlike the Galaxy of Dreams album, Liquicity has gathered a series of melancholic, chilled and mellow tracks that form a harmonious journey through todays Liquid Drum and Bass. 14 exclusive new tracks by artists such as Bachelors of Science, Bcee, Maduk, Keeno, Fliwo and Champion.
